with version stable 5.1 5.0
with base    readline
with elect   xinetd '' '' for running TFTP-server in inet-mode
with also    --prefix=$DEST_DIR/$SPELL/usr
with role    network/tftp
with trait   console server
with trait   broke
with source  http://www.kernel.org/pub/software/network/tftp/tftp-hpa-$VERSION.tar.bz2
with info    omit 20130101
with info    last 20110625
with info    home http://www.kernel.org/pub/software/network/tftp
with info    freecode tftp-hpa
with fill    tftp-server
with info    cite 'enhanced version of the BSD TFTP client and server
It possesses a number of bugfixes and enhancements over the original. 
It has been made portable and will work on pretty much any modern Unix variant.
Good for use with pxelinux from syslinux in order to network boot.'
